<br>
<div class= "card-instruction">
  <h2>Congratulations! You completed the exercise!</h2>

  <div>
    <p>Attempts: <%= @submission.attempts_count %></p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <% if @submission.attempts_count > 3 %>
      <p>If you took too many attempts to complete the exercise, here are some tips to improve your performance:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Read the instructions carefully before attempting the exercise.</li>
        <li>Break down the problem into smaller parts.</li>
        <li>Use debugging tools to find and fix errors in your code.</li>
      </ul>
    <% else %>
      <p>Great job! You completed the exercice with ease.</p>
    <% end %>
    <p>Gained experience : +<%= @submission.exercice.exp %> exp</p>
  </div>
</div>
<br>

<div>
  <%= link_to "Retry Exercise", new_exercice_submission_path(exercice_id: @submission.exercice_id), class:"btn btn-primary" %>
  <br>
  <br>
  <div class="social-media-sharing">
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-twitter"> <i class="fa-brands fa-square-twitter"></i> Share on Twitter</a>
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-facebook"> <i class="fa-brands fa-square-facebook"></i> Share on Facebook</a>
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-linkedin"> <i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i> Share on LinkedIn</a>
  </div>
</div>

  <% if current_user.beginners_luck? %>
    <div class="flash flash-warning alert alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
      <span><strong>üèÜ Achivement completed !</strong>&nbsp;</span>
      <a data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
        <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  <% end %>
